name: DevFeeds
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, what's in the news?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Listen to daily tech updates from your favorite source. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
All the concise feeds right at your tip to keep you updated, engaged in a world where keeping up with all the ruckus in the industry is overwhelming.
This skill's main motive is to provide you with the byte-sized information so that you can keep track of your surroundings. It's aimed at every developer/geek/nerd/student desiring tech news from all over the globe in under a minute.
